  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">11 MOBILE ANALYTICS We use mobile analytics software to allow us to better understand the functionality of our mobile software on your phone This software may record information such as how often you use the App the events that occur within the App aggregated usage performance data and where the App was downloaded from We do not link the information we store within the analytics software to any Personally Identifiable Information you submit within the App</evidence>
